  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个流程图，展示患者从社区到住院的完整路径，以及导致急诊滞留的瓶颈机制。核心是想解释access block是怎么形成的。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Community",
        "ED_Arrival",
        "access block mechanism"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，所以起点是Community？患者先到社区，然后通过GP或者直接去急诊？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Community",
        "GP",
        "ED_Arrival"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，两条路径：一条是Community到GP再到ED_Arrival，另一条是Community直接到ED_Arrival。GP那个节点标注成\"GP / primary care\"，用蓝色系。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Community",
        "GP",
        "ED_Arrival"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我把Community设为neutral灰色，GP用cth样式蓝色填充，ED_Arrival保持neutral。接下来是ED_Treat？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Community",
        "GP",
        "ED_Arrival",
        "ED_Treat"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "ED_Arrival之后是ED_Treat，标注\"ED assessment & treatment\"，这个用state样式，红色系，表示这是关键状态节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ED_Treat",
        "ED_Arrival"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "ED_Treat用红色填充，stroke是#b71c1c。然后流向Decision to admit？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ED_Treat",
        "Admission"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，Decision to admit是neutral灰色，然后到Inpatient stay，这个也是state样式红色。接着是Ready for discharge，回到neutral。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Admission",
        "Inpatient",
        "Ready"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "主线完成了：Community → GP → ED_Arrival → ED_Treat → Decision to admit → Inpatient stay → Ready for discharge。现在瓶颈部分怎么体现？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Community",
        "GP",
        "ED_Arrival",
        "ED_Treat",
        "Admission",
        "Inpatient",
        "Ready"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "关键在这里：Ready for discharge之后不是直接出院，而是分出两个blockages。一个是Aged care placement，标注\"capacity constraint\"；另一个是NDIS supports / accommodation，标注\"delay / mismatch\"。这两个都是risk样式，橙色虚线框。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Ready",
        "Block_Aged",
        "Block_NDIS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "所以Block_Aged和Block_NDIS是并行从Ready分出来的？不是顺序关系？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Ready",
        "Block_Aged",
        "Block_NDIS"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，两个独立的约束条件，哪个卡住都会导致滞留。用risk样式，橙色填充#fff3e0，stroke是#e65100，还要加stroke-dasharray虚线效果。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Block_Aged",
        "Block_NDIS",
        "risk"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "加上了，两个橙色虚线框的blockages。现在access block mechanism怎么画？是反馈回路？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Block_Aged",
        "Block_NDIS",
        "access block mechanism"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，这是核心。Block_Aged要有一条虚线连回Inpatient，标注\"occupancy feedback loop\"。表示老年护理床位卡住，病人回不去，住院部床位被占满。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Block_Aged",
        "Inpatient",
        "feedback"
